<pre><code>&lt;CustomAction Id="XXXX" Property="TARGETDIR" Value="XXX"/&gt; &lt;InstallExecuteSequence&gt;       &lt;Custom Action="XXXX"  Before="CostFinalize"&gt;&lt;/Custom&gt; &lt;/InstallExecuteSequence&gt; </code></pre>  <p>This custom action is changing the value of TARGETDIR property in normal installation for WiX installer. But, it is not changing property value in Passive mode of installation of WiX installer.</p>